<h2 class="learn-heading">Learn: Release Word ‚ú® "Free"</h2>

<p>When your dog is in a sustained behavior (like a stay), they need a clear signal that it's okay to get up and move. This is where the release word "free" comes in. When you say "free," your dog should feel like a kid on the last day of school. Freedom is the reward!</p>

